{"tid":172332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚所有連登膠徒，是日小丑教祟拜","createTime":"2017-03-25T23:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T12:05:17.000Z","uid":3261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad91160d4cddbbbe68ae54d2634e266a53cd7721","tid":172332,"uid":3261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T23:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m2G4i49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm2G4i49.jpg&h=1159831d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">小丑教禱文</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我們在連登的神，<br />\n願人都尊神的名為膠；<br />\n<br />\n願神的國降臨；<br />\n<br />\n願神的旨意行在地上，<br />\n<br />\n如同行在連登。<br />\n<br />\n我們日用的膠幣，<br />\n<br />\n求神今日賜給我們。<br />\n<br />\n又求饒恕我們的假膠，<br />\n<br />\n因為我們饒恕假膠的人。<br />\n<br />\n不叫我們遇見試探，<br />\n<br />\n拯救我們脫離耶教。<br />\n<br />\n因為國度、權柄、榮耀、<br />\n<br />\n全是神的，直到永遠。膠們。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aef4c02b449542ff45f9b00d02c531924f55170","tid":172332,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T23:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516dbca0ca3994f6c6455b9fc38de3056316a896","tid":172332,"uid":97947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T23:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b6